                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Diagnostic Trouble Code Description</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>131 APS signal voltage was &#60; 0.146 volts for more than 0.5 sec*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>132 APS signal voltage was more than 4.55 volts for more than 0.5 sec*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>133 APS signal in-range fault*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>134 APS and IVS disagree*</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>135 Idle validation switch circuit fault - 50% APS only</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="6" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>*If diagnostic trouble code is set, engine operation will default to run at low
